121
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:40,080
All the while the disease ravaged on, killing over 300 million people  in the 20th century alone. 

122
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:46,900
In 1966 the World Health Organization decided  that humanity had to come together in a final, major effort. 

123
00:07:46,900 --> 00:07:51,840
A global "smallpox news network," based on residents in hotspots, was created 

124
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:54,500
