125
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:59,720
Cases were encircled, vaccines given, preventing further spread. 

126
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:06,260
Smallpox only infects humans, so if we stopped the human transmission chain, we would starve the virus.

127
00:08:06,260 --> 00:08:09,730
